<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="224" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="9" pageNumber="224">Distribution, phenology and biology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="9" pageNumber="224">
Recorded only for the DRC and Tanzania. While there is no certainty regarding the precise type locality, the coordinates of the nearest settlement (Kambove) serve to indicate its presence in the DRC (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 25" captionStartId="F14" captionText="Figure 25. Distribution of Astochia species: A. africana, A. armata, A. neavensis." figureDoi="10.3897/AfrInvertebr.60.38432.figure25" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/346349" pageId="9" pageNumber="224" tableDoi="10.3897/AfrInvertebr.60.38432.figure25">Fig. 25</figureCitation>
). Collected in October and November (Table 
<tableCitation captionStartId="T1" httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/77ABE6B430CB8ADF8FCB922543B38124" pageId="9" pageNumber="224" tableUuid="77ABE6B430CB8ADF8FCB922543B38124">1</tableCitation>
). No biological information is available.
</paragraph>
